If the initiative type is set to "New Feature" and you try to import into a portfolio, the New Feature is imported by default as an Epic.  

You can manually change it to Initiative during the import, but then the Epics that are linked to it are not linked as part of the import.

This can be resolved manually, but it is very time and error prone.

