JPO currently uses some kind of client-side scrollbar, rather than a standard scrollable page.

As a result, any attempt to capture the page (print, print-to-pdf, browser add-on to screencap full page) gives only the information [above the fold|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Above_the_fold].
Lacking the ability to export the backlog into any alternative usable format (eg. PDF, CSV, Excel, Word), at least let us export what we see using client (browser) tools.

